How do you create a product feedback survey?

, you can target specific user groups to reach the most appropriate audience and request their feedback as they engage with your product. After you install the Sprig app, you can create your survey in just a few clicks. Then narrow down your target audience, so users see your survey exactly when you want them to see it.
What questions should you ask in a product survey?

The questions you ask in your survey should relate to the problem you’re trying to solve. For instance, let’s say you want to know why customers aren’t completing your onboarding flow. You might ask an open-ended question, such as, “Tell us more about why you haven’t been back to our app.” If you need additional guidance in designing your product survey,
How do you create a user research survey?

Creating a user research survey is simple with the right tools. With Sprig, you can easily create user research surveys from scratch or with the help of a template. Whichever you choose, the Sprig Study Editor tool will help streamline customization based on your survey’s goals. Once your survey questions are ready, you’ll decide on your distribution channels, such as web or mobile app. Then, set filters and triggers so your target audience receives the survey at the right time after interacting with your product.
How long should user surveys be?

Make sure your surveys take no more than a few minutes to complete. Users shouldn’t feel like they're taking a test or writing an essay when responding to survey questions. Otherwise, they might get frustrated and abandon the survey halfway through.
What is the best survey method?

Several methods can be used to gather feedback about your product. However, in-product surveys are a proven, effective tool for collecting feedback directly from users while they engage with your product. These types of surveys allow you to capture real-time insights from your customers. Sprig’s in-product Surveys help you understand user friction points so you know exactly what you need to improve to give your users a better experience.
What is the best survey software?

The best survey software lets you request and receive feedback without distracting users from your product. With Sprig, you get an all-in-one survey solution that fits right into your product. This way, you can gather feedback in real-time. You can also personalize your surveys so they reflect your brand identity and resonate well with customers.
